      <title>用hexo建静态博客全过程</title>
      <link href="/2023/03/12/tips/hexo/hexobuild/"/>
      <url>/2023/03/12/tips/hexo/hexobuild/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="用hexo建静态博客全过程"><a href="#用hexo建静态博客全过程" class="headerlink" title="用hexo建静态博客全过程"></a>用hexo建静态博客全过程</h2><h3 id="一、准备"><a href="#一、准备" class="headerlink" title="一、准备"></a>一、准备</h3><ol><li>环境：node.js。推荐安装12.0版本。安装和环境配置的教程网上很多，不写了😉<br>  <a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download/">官网下载</a></li><li>工具：git。用于上传代码到github。一般无脑next，教程很多，也不写了😬<br>  <a href="https://git.p2hp.com/">下载</a></li></ol><h3 id="二、本地创建项目"><a href="#二、本地创建项目" class="headerlink" title="二、本地创建项目."></a>二、本地创建项目.</h3><p>1.安装hexo包：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli  </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.创建项目文件夹(Win)：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir xxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3.新建一个hexo<br><code>hexo init</code></p><p>4.创建文章：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new [layout] \&lt;title&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#以下命令会创建一个 source/about/me.md 文件，</span><br><span class="line">#同时 Front Matter 中的 title 为 &quot;About me&quot;。</span><br><span class="line">#注意title是必需要的。</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page --path about/me &quot;About me&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>不设置layout，则使用配置文件中的default_layout</p><p>5.构建项目</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>6.预览</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>9.下载主题，把它放到 &#x2F;themes 目录下</p><p>10.修改_config.yml<br>theme: </p><p>11.重新生成</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="二、部署到github"><a href="#二、部署到github" class="headerlink" title="二、部署到github"></a>二、部署到github</h3><p>1.安装插件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.在github上创建仓库<code>xxx.github.io</code>,xxx就是你github的用户名</p><p>4.修改_config.yml</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 其中xxx就是你github的用户名，branch推荐用main</span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: &#x27;git&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">  repo: git@github.com:xxx/xxx.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3.部署</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4.线上访问<br><code>xxx.github.io</code></p><h3 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h3><ul><li><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty/?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click&vd_source=b17120e43489c29aaaccb049e11aef82">手把手教你从0开始搭建自己的个人博客 |无坑版视频教程| hexo</a></li><li><a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs">hexo官网</a></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
